{{- /*
Minimal traefik values for the managed-Keycloak VPN flow. The chart
defaults already cover most of what we need (HA replicas, web→websecure
redirect); kubeaid-cli only needs to point traefik's Service at the
HCloud control-plane LB so external traffic to keycloak.<dns> /
netbird.<dns> lands on the same LB the apiserver is exposed through.

The cert-manager ClusterIssuer renders an http01 solver against the
`traefik` ingressClassName — see values-cert-manager.yaml.tmpl. */ -}}
traefik:
  service:
    annotations:
      load-balancer.hetzner.cloud/use-private-ip: "false"
      load-balancer.hetzner.cloud/uses-proxyprotocol: "false"
